1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 2=

4
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:53,800
I wish I could paint too.

5
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:56,600
Then I'd get to see Qiao Xiaomi
all the time in class.

6
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:00,160
You can pretend to be me
and go to class.

7
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,240
Relax.

8
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,400
No one's going to figure it out.

9
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:07,040
There are so many students

10
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,000
in the Art Department.

11
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,400
Just get to know her first.

12
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,680
You'll have plenty of chances later.

13
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:11,720
Trust me.

14
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,680
Take it easy.

15
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,320
Hold this for me.

16
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:18,880
Qin Yu!

17
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,560
Ji Ran, hold that for me.

18
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,840
I'm going after Xiaoduo!

19
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:41,150
(Qin Yu)

20
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:43,000
Qin Yu?

21
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:46,200
You're Qin Yu, the guy who always wins

22
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,600
first place in the city's
youth painting competition?

23
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:48,560
I...

24
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,080
I've seen every one of your paintings.

25
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,480
I love them all.

26
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,520
I've always wanted to meet you.

27
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,880
I never expected

28
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,480
that not only are you a great artist,

29
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,960
you're handsome too.

30
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,440
My name is Qin Yu.

31
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,520
A fire three years ago

32
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,040
changed the fate of all four of us.

33
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,960
Where's Xiaoduo?

34
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,120
Ye Xiaoduo, the girl

35
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,080
you're looking for, is dead.

36
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,040
My face was disfigured.

37
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:25,360
My best friend, Ji Ran, died.

38
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,960
I know I saved

39
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,760
the girl I loved, Ye Xiaoduo.

40
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,640
So why was it

41
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:33,840
her half-sister, Qiao Xiaomi
who survived?

42
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,320
To find out the truth,

43
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,720
I had surgery to look like Ji Ran.

44
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,200
The first person who fell for it

45
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,560
was her brother, Qiao Zhiwei.

46
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,680
Unbelievable.

47
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,680
You look exactly like him.

48
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,360
But

49
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,280
I do have my strengths.

50
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,040
I'm loyal.

51
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,800
It's been three years.

52
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,680
I've missed you every single day.

53
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,400
I've come back to marry you.

54
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,760
I'm your fiancé.

55
00:03:28,510 --> 00:03:30,360
(Background Investigation Report)

56
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,360
Qin Yu.

57
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,760
Who are you, really?

58
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,560
Miss Qiao,

59
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,160
Dr. Chen has been waiting
for you for a while.

60
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,280
He's here again?

61
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:42,960
Let's do it another day.

62
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,760
I'm still exhausted.

63
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,040
But I looked him up.

64
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,560
He does have quite a reputation

65
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,760
in the field of psychology.

66
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,840
Beneath those bold red strokes
lies a sense of unease.

67
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:54,560
Yet beneath the blue tones,
there's a search for balance.

68
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,400
What a fascinating contradiction.

69
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,720
You must be Miss Qiao,

70
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,720
the owner of this gallery.

71
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,160
Hello.

72
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,280
What can I do for you?

73
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:06,840
Let me introduce myself.

74
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:08,440
My name is Chen Yue.

75
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,000
I'm a psychologist.

76
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,800
My specialty is research in art therapy.

77
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,040
Therapy?

78
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,360
That's right.

79
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,400
My team studies

80
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,040
and develops artworks

81
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,760
that help people process emotions

82
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,960
and better understand their inner world.

83
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,760
I've noticed

84
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:33,000
that many pieces in your gallery

85
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,640
align closely

86
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,160
with my research interests.

87
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,400
So I was wondering
whether you'd be interested

88
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,760
in collaborating with us

89
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:45,600
on art therapy programs
or related research projects

90
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,760
for specific groups.

91
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,360
That does sound interesting.

92
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,640
Oh, right.

93
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,240
I almost forgot to mention,

94
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,240
all of my projects are nonprofit.

95
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,760
There's no compensation involved.

96
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,000
If you're not interested and say no,

97
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,600
I won't be offended.

98
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,280
Miss Qiao, Mr. Qin is here again.

99
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,840
This is already the third day in a row.

100
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,160
Miss Qiao, where are you going?

101
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,800
I can't stop him, so I'm leaving.

102
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,960
But this is your company.

103
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,200
If anyone should leave,
it should be him.

104
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,640
Good point.

105
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,960
Then make him leave.

106
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,360
Yeah.

107
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,600
Why should I leave?

108
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:56,080
Take me away.

109
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:59,840
Take me far into the future.

110
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:01,440
I've told you several times already.

111
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,120
Miss Qiao really isn't here.

112
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,840
Take me away!

113
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:07,960
Cut the act.

114
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:13,040
Take me far into the future.

115
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,120
Stop acting!

116
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:14,960
Let him perform.

117
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,400
Xiaomi.

118
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,080
Come with me.

119
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,280
These are from three years ago.

120
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,480
After that incident,

121
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,160
I forgot everything.

122
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,280
I even forgot who I was.

123
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,240
My fiancé,

124
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,080
who keeps saying he loves me,

125
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,760
where were you

126
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:04,360
when I cried in front of a blank canvas

127
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,560
until sunrise?

128
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:10,560
Where were you
when I was in so much pain

129
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,760
that I couldn't sleep all night?

130
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,600
When I looked in the mirror
and saw my scars,

131
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,960
when even I couldn't stand
the sight of myself,

132
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,360
where were you?

133
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,880
Even if you're not lying,

134
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,960
then tell me this.

135
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,920
Why did you abandon me halfway through?

136
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,360
I know I owe you so much.

137
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,480
More than I could ever repay.

138
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,960
Xiaomi.

139
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,000
Give me two months.

140
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,760
Within two months,

141
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,440
I'll help you get your memories back,

142
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,360
pick up your paintbrush again,

143
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,400
and finish every painting here.

144
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,280
If I do it,

145
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,080
can you give me one more chance?

146
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,440
Let me spend the rest of my life,

147
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,040
everything I have,

148
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:29,520
making it up to you

149
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,360
and staying by your side.

150
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,200
Alright.

151
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:43,680
I promise.

152
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,400
Two months.

153
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:49,840
If you fail,

154
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,400
then get out of my life.

155
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:09,880
Zhiwei,

156
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,320
why the long face?

157
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,160
What's bothering you?

158
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,800
Tell me. Maybe I can help.

159
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:19,360
You help me?

160
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:22,800
Want another designer bag?

161
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,360
So that's what you think of me?

162
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,280
Stop beating around the bush.

163
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,680
Just say what you want.

164
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:34,680
Zhiwei,

165
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:38,080
I heard the gallery's
curatorial department is hiring.

166
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,080
That's exactly what I studied overseas.

167
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,800
As long as you say the word,

168
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,280
Xiaomi won't refuse.

169
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,320
Why don't you just ask Xiaomi yourself?

170
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,920
You know perfectly well

171
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,280
she doesn't remember anything.

172
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,040
Zhiwei,

173
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,760
if you're willing to help me,

174
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,480
I can help you

175
00:09:57,760 --> 00:10:00,120
take back everything
that belongs to you.

176
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,860
♪We say good morning,
we say good night♪

177
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:41,280
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

178
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,770
♪The sweeter it is,
the luckier we seem♪

179
00:10:44,770 --> 00:10:48,760
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

180
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,860
♪Let me go, set me free♪

181
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:55,900
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

182
00:10:56,440 --> 00:11:01,850
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

183
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,340
♪The freedom you gave me♪

184
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:08,980
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

185
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,510
♪Love can barely move forward♪

186
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:16,300
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

187
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:19,630
♪The closeness I long for♪

188
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:24,020
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

189
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:26,250
♪I don't want to break free♪

190
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:31,620
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

